How to Build ZK

* First you have to install Ant 1.6.2 or above.

* If you are using Windows, you have to install Cygwin.

* The required jar files are not shipped with this distribution. However,
  you can download them from the Subversion server at the following URL.

  http://svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/zk1/trunk/dist/lib/ext/

* Alernatively, you retrieve any particular version of source codes from
  the Subversion sever at the following URL.

  http://svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/zk1/releases
